---
---

<section class="success-stories reveal" id="work">
    <p class="success-stories__vertical-text">SUCCESS STORY</p>

    <div class="success-stories__content">
        <div class="success-stories__cards">
            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-1">
                <div class="success-stories__card-image"></div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">40% cost reduction</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SAAS PLATFORM REBUILD</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Architecture overhaul of a multi-tenant SaaS platform serving 200+ enterprise clients. Migrated from monolithic PHP to distributed Node.js, tripling throughput.</p>
                <div class="success-stories__card-footer">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Architecture</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-2">
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">12-person team</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SCALE-UP TEAM BUILDING</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Built an engineering team from scratch. Established hiring pipelines, onboarding, and code review culture that cut deploy time from weeks to hours.</p>
                <div class="success-stories__card-footer">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Leadership</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-3">
                <div class="success-stories__card-image"></div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">99.99% uptime</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">CLOUD MIGRATION</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Migrated a legacy monolith to cloud-native microservices on AWS — zero downtime, 5M records preserved, 60% infrastructure cost reduction.</p>
                <div class="success-stories__card-footer">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Infrastructure</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-4">
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">3x conversions</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">E-COMMERCE RELAUNCH</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Rebuilt a failing e-commerce platform end-to-end, delivering 3x conversion rate improvement and 60% faster page loads.</p>
                <div class="success-stories__card-footer">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Product Dev</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__cta-row">
            <a class="success-stories__cta" href="#contact">BOOK A CALL</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .success-stories {
        position: relative;
        padding: 80px 144px 48px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: stretch;
        gap: 0;

        &__vertical-text {
            position: absolute;
            left: 10px;
            top: 48px;
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            color: rgba(0, 135, 95, 0.06);
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            writing-mode: vertical-lr;
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            line-height: 1;
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
            user-select: none;
            max-height: calc(100% - 96px);
        }

        &__content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 48px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        &__cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        &__card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
            border-radius: 0;
            background: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;

            &:hover {
                border-color: rgba(0, 135, 95, 0.25);
            }
            padding: 28px 24px;
        }

        &__card-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 140px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 135, 95, 0.06), var(--clr-bg-surface) 70%);
        }

        &__card-metric {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
        }

        &__card-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        &__card-desc {
            font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            flex: 1;
        }

        &__card-footer {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        &__card-tag {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 9px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;

            &::before {
                content: '';
                display: inline-block;
                width: 6px;
                height: 6px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background-color: var(--clr-accent);
                flex-shrink: 0;
            }
        }

        &__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        &__cta {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            background: var(--clr-accent);
            border-radius: 0;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                opacity: 0.88;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 2rem;

            &__vertical-text {
                display: none;
            }

            &__cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 1.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
